Name: ``fmin-auglag``
Description: Augmented Lagrangian trust region method for minimizing scalar valued multivariate function. See https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.fmin_auglag.html

Name: ``fmin-auglag-bfgs``
Description: Augmented Lagrangian trust region method for minimizing scalar valued multivariate function. Uses BFGS to approximate Hessian. See https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.fmin_auglag.html

Name: ``lsq-auglag``
Description: Least squares augmented Lagrangian for constrained optimizationSee https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.lsq_auglag.html

Name: ``lsq-exact``
Description: Trust region least squares, similar to the `trf` method in scipySee https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.lsqtr.html

Name: ``fmintr``
Description: Trust region method for minimizing scalar valued multivariate function. See https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.fmintr.html

Name: ``fmintr-bfgs``
Description: Trust region method for minimizing scalar valued multivariate function. Uses BFGS to approximate the Hessian. See https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.fmintr.html

Name: ``sgd``
Description: Stochastic gradient descent with Nesterov momentumSee https://desc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/_api/optimize/desc.optimize.sgd.html

Name: ``scipy-bfgs``
Description: BFGS quasi-newton method with line search. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-bfgs.html

Name: ``scipy-dogleg``
Description: Trust region method with dogleg step. Hessian must be positive definite. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-dogleg.html

Name: ``scipy-trust-exact``
Description: Trust region method using 'exact' method to solve subproblem. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-trustexact.html

Name: ``scipy-trust-ncg``
Description: Trust region method using conjugate gradient to solve subproblem. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-trustncg.html

Name: ``scipy-trust-krylov``
Description: Trust region method using Krylov iterations to solve subproblem. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-trustkrylov.html

Name: ``scipy-trf``
Description: Trust region least squares method. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.optimize.least_squares.html

Name: ``scipy-lm``
Description: Levenberg-Marquardt implicit trust region method. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.optimize.least_squares.html

Name: ``scipy-dogbox``
Description: Dogleg method with box shaped trust region. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.optimize.least_squares.html

Name: ``scipy-trust-constr``
Description: Trust region interior point method. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-trustconstr.html

Name: ``scipy-SLSQP``
Description: Sequential least squares programming method. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/optimize.minimize-slsqp.html
